{"tid":884060,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"差估署︰九龍細單位9月平均售價跌穿600萬元","createTime":"2018-10-31T10:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T01:53:13.000Z","uid":28245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5a72966de7741190e9ca0b05671dd638eabe97","tid":884060,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:05:01.000Z","msg":"據差餉物業估價署最新數據，各區實用面積431方呎以下細單位平均每方呎售價全面向下。其中以九龍區跌價最勁。該區截至9月份呎價約13,711港元，按月跌約6%，以實用面積約430方呎單位計算，平均售價約589萬元，跌穿600萬元，為今年2月後最低。 <br />\n<br />\n至於港島區細單位跌幅亦大。該區平均每方呎售價約16,640元，按月挫約4.2%。以實用面積約430方呎單位計算，平均售價約715萬元，為今年3月後最低。 <br />\n<br />\n而新界區同類單位平均呎價約13,036元，按月下調約2.59%。以實用面積約430方呎單位計算，平均售價約560萬元，屬今年4月後最低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n9月只係開始 黎緊第4季先精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係200尺以下單位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc32e80bfb6e95fde1b494116f9093a4f27f941","tid":884060,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396d83eef09b29fd38f64ae602fec86122b8f48c","tid":884060,"uid":21661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc32e80bfb6e95fde1b494116f9093a4f27f941","tid":884060,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:06:26.000Z","msg":"計唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"sorry 唔計喎"},{"pid":"dcb3f790c07400af9575261ae75cbda6c5dde6a8","tid":884060,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"呢個只係9月數據 岩岩開始加息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10月 分分鍾有10%<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7f59ab6caac5ae3549ce76316045675c2a4618d","tid":884060,"uid":164730,"like